    <h1>Faceted Navigation</h1>
    <p class="description">A filtering system on e-commerce and content sites that generates hundreds of thousands of near-duplicate URLs — the most common source of <strong>crawl budget waste</strong> and duplicate content on large sites.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
